frames.caption: In a whimsical scene, miniature figures are depicted working on a large dessert, arranging strawberries on top of a chocolate-covered tart. The figures use ladders and baskets, creating the illusion of a bustling construction site. The background features a blurred array of strawberries, enhancing the playful atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a creative, fantastical world where tiny people are engaged in assembling a dessert. The focus is on the interaction between the figures and the oversized strawberries, creating a surreal and imaginative setting.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures working on a dessert topped with strawberries and chocolate. The tiny workers use ladders to climb the dessert, carrying baskets and arranging the strawberries. The setting is playful and imaginative, blending culinary art with fantasy.
frames.description: The scene is set on a wooden surface, featuring a dessert garnished with large strawberry slices and a glossy chocolate topping. Miniature figures are engaged in assembling the dessert, creating a surreal and imaginative atmosphere.
